    "course_title": "INTRODUCTION TO THEATRE FOR CULTURAL AND SOCIAL AWARENESS",
    "description": "Analysis of sensitive subject matter in U.S. workplace and school/community settings through theatre and drama. Examines race relations, cultural diversity, gender, sexual orientation and other topics in plays, films, and current events. Develops theatrical models to encourage healthy dialogue.",
